com%2Fgroups%2F2948245218793925%2Fpermalink%2F2948542105430903%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=bbc92c3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2948245218793925/permalink/2948542105430903/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n搜索資源<br />\n義務搜索隊: 已有5隊在山搜索(6 + 6 + 3 + ? + 3)<br />\n上山人士請以zello作溝通工具(<a href=\"https://zello.com/channels/k/hGeoi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzello.com%2Fchannels%2Fk%2FhGeoi&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=e09e401c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zello.com/channels/k/hGeoi</a>) <br />\n<br />\n航拍小隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/2948245218793925/permalink/2948412122110568/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2948245218793925%2Fpermalink%2F2948412122110568%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=504cf84a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/2948245218793925/permalink/2948412122110568/</a><br />\n<br />\n0330: 消防已暫停搜救(已確認)<br />\n0420: 雲梯及山拯救到達山頂<br />\n0435: 消防換更，共3架，全滿人 <br />\n0440: GFS待天氣無霧再出發<br />\n<br />\n失蹤人士懷疑身處路徑極為危險，新手或單獨人士切勿上山，建議上山人士多人一組及帶備合適裝備 <br />\n<br />\n當事人電腦曾瀏覽路線<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=SP35k3wL-Xk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSP35k3wL-Xk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=e8291293\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=SP35k3wL-Xk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"}}